<br>
Move the little gauntlet cursor over the area that you need to disarm. If it's a trap on the floor, just put your cursor over it. If it's a chest, put your cursor over that until it lights up.<br>
<br>
Following me so far? Hope so.<br>
<br>
Now then... Right Click it! You will see a lil menu pop up. See that lil thing on the right of the pinwheel, it looks like a bear trap. Click that. It'll let you choose to disarm, recover, or flag the trap. <br>
<br>
To Unlock a Chest or door, highlight the object, and choose the Lock that isn't Locked. <br>
<br>
